name: A Dress- 8 inch by 8 inch original mixed media painting
description: This original painting is done on an 8 inch by 8 inch gallery wrapped canvas (1 1/2 inches deep). It is part of my Dress series. The following materials were used in creating this painting; acrylic paint, Japanese rice paper, fabric, lace, and pearls.
